303  double getTotalHeat() {
304  double hliq;
305  if (dischargeTemperature < vaporizingTemperature) {
306  // H_liq=m_li×C_pl×(t_lo-t_li )
307  hliq = chargeFeedRate * specificHeatLiquid * (dischargeTemperature - initialTemperature);
308  } else {
309  // H_liq=m_li×C_pl×(t_lv-t_li )+%lv×m_lt×[h_lv+C_pv (t_lo-T_lv )]+(1-%lv)×C_pl (t_lo-t_lv)
310  hliq = chargeFeedRate *
311  (specificHeatLiquid * (vaporizingTemperature - initialTemperature)
312  + percentVaporized * (latentHeat + specificHeatVapor * (dischargeTemperature - vaporizingTemperature))
313  + (1 - percentVaporized) * specificHeatLiquid * (dischargeTemperature - vaporizingTemperature));
314  }
315 
316  double heatReacted = 0.0;
317  if (thermicReactionType == LoadChargeMaterial::ThermicReactionType::ENDOTHERMIC) {
318  heatReacted = chargeFeedRate * percentReacted * reactionHeat;
319  }
320  totalHeat = hliq + heatReacted + additionalHeat;
321  return totalHeat;
322  }
323
